This HTML5 webpage is designed to be a professional profile for Jon Edlund. It incorporates a clean, responsive layout using embedded CSS and interactive elements with JavaScript, adhering to your request for a concise "half-page" design.

I have integrated information found on the Central Wyoming College (CWC) website, specifically highlighting the program's focus on **ASE Certification** and the **hands-on nature** of the Automotive Technology department.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
